# Repository Map Index

- `app/`: Expo Router entrypoints and screen composition.
- `features/`: Domain feature UI and feature-scoped logic.
- `components/`: Shared UI building blocks; `components/ui/` for design-system primitives.
- `hooks/`: Reusable interaction/state hooks (including topo gestures and viewport logic).
- `services/`: Data loading/parsing and integration utilities (for example SVG path loading).
- `src/theme/`: Theme tokens and style system source.
- `docs/` and `topo-preview-ui-decision.md`: behavioral and product decision docs.

## File Placement Heuristics

- New screen route -> `app/...`
- Reusable UI primitive -> `components/ui/...`
- Feature-specific view/state -> `features/<FeatureName>/...`
- Data transform/loader/parser -> `services/...`
- Cross-screen reusable logic -> `hooks/...`
